{
  "stem": "10698.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wrote to the Jewish newspaper, forward to New York, that two sisters are from wherever, then the first names, and all, are looking for a brother Leo Fromer, and an aunt Rhea Levingrup.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My Aunt Rhea was sitting having breakfast, and I knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her sister-in-law comes in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She says, look, is that your family?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rhea Levingrup lived in-- in New York-- in Brooklyn, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she-- my brother lived in-- in-- in New York, in Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said is that you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She started to cry, my sister's children are alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they got in touch with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, I found out that my oldest brother, that ran away with his wife and child to Russia-- because, you know, they were killing people that were-- my brother was running the first aid station also during the bombarding.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they-- they were alive, and they came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they got in touch with my brother, here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's when I found out that they are-- they are alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they started to send us packages with food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So between the-- between the better ration card, and the packages, we were not starving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were-- we-- so I met my husband, and we got married in 1946.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Berlin.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time by then, we rented an apartment to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and we did the wedding right there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We invited some people, and some people that were, you know, German-Jewish people that came back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they helped us out with putting together little foods and things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they opened up a kosher butcher stores, and we could buy it on the ration cards, also.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
